keyFacts: The FBI conducted a witness interview in Beverly Hills, CA from February 26-29, 2020 as part of the Epstein investigation.
Travel voucher 11061344-1(1) was approved on March 24, 2020 for this investigative trip.
The trip had total expenses of $1,059.52 against an estimated cost of $1,621.65.
The document indicates ongoing investigative activity in the Epstein case as of early 2020.
The travel was specifically coded as 'R2ONYS13402 - Epstein Investigation - Witness interview'.
